  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT86">
<l>uḷaṉkaṇṭāy naṉṉeñcē yuttama ṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>muḷaṉkaṇṭā yuḷḷuvā ruḷḷat tuḷaṉkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>taṉṉoppāṉ tāṉā yuḷaṉkāṇ tamiyēṟku</l>
<l>meṉṉoppārk kīca ṉimai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O good heart! See, the Highest [Lord] is [there to protect].</l>
<l>He is [there to protect] at all times, see! See, He is in the minds of those</l>
<l rend="indent">who think of [Him]!</l>
<l>See, the Lord who is His [own] equal is [there to protect].</l>
<l>He is the Supreme Lord for me, a destitute person, and for the likes of me!</l>
<l rend="indent">Be enlightened!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
